name: First run over 5K
description: Started cramping at 2.7k which is weird: didn’t eat for 4.5 hours and drank a Gatorade 2 hours before my run, and had a small glass of water (75ml roughly) 10 mins before the run. Small break at 3.6 when I reached food basics, then didn’t cramp at all the rest of the run which was TIGHT. Calves defs hurting after this, hopefully gonna get used to running this far soon
